trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustRelationshipInformation" /> class contains information for a trust relationship between a pair of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> or <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: La classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustRelationshipInformation" /> contient des informations pour une relation d'approbation entre une paire d'objets <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> ou <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" />.

trans-unit.source: Obtains the name of the source <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> or <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> objects for this trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Obtient le nom des objets sources <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> ou <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> pour cette relation d'approbation.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the name of the source <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> or <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> objects for this trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Chaîne qui contient le nom des objets sources <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> ou <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> pour cette relation d'approbation.

trans-unit.source: Obtains the name of the target <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> or <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> objects for this trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Obtient le nom des objets cible <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> ou <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> pour cette relation d'approbation.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the name of the target <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> or <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> objects for this trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Chaîne qui contient le nom des objets cible <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> ou <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> pour cette relation d'approbation.

trans-unit.source: Obtains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustDirection" /> objects for this trust relationship relative to the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> or <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> objects that created the trust.
trans-unit.target: Obtient les objets <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustDirection" /> pour cette relation d'approbation relativement aux objets <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> ou <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> qui ont créé l'approbation.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustDirection" /> value for this trust relationship relative to the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> or <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> objects that created the trust.
trans-unit.target: Valeur <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustDirection" /> pour cette relation d'approbation relative aux objets <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> ou <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> qui ont créé l'approbation.

trans-unit.source: Obtains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustType" /> object of the trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Obtient l'objet <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustType" /> de la relation d'approbation.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustType" /> value that represents the type of the trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Valeur <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustType" /> qui représente le type de relation d'approbation.
